QuestData.Title: Prisoners
QuestData.Description: The Twilight cultist dropped this key. Use it to free the Alliance prisoners in the cages inside of L'ghorek.$B$BHurry before the prisoners become sacrifices to whatever lurks below!
QuestData.RewardText: A job well done. Now you don't need to worry about what would have happened to them if you hadn't been around.$B$BThe last one was even appreciative enough to give you a reward they'd kept hidden on their person.
